<HEADLINE> Bank of China Int'l (UK) Limited to Begin Trading </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LONDON, January 2 (Xinhua) -- Bank of China International (UK)
Limited announced here today that it has obtained all necessary
regulatory consents to begin trading in the new year.
</P>
<P>
The newly established merchant bank has been granted Authorized
Institution status by the Bank of England and has been accepted as
an authorized member of the Securities and Futures Authority.
</P>
<P>
Bank of China International (UK) Limited will offer a wide
range of merchant banking services to European investors wishing
to invest in China and Hong Kong including debt and equity capital
markets, structured finance and corporate advisory services.
</P>
