<TEXT>
<P>
JOHANNESBURG, January 2 (Xinhua) -- The African National
Congress (ANC) of South Africa will celebrate its 85th
anniversary with a national rally on January 12, ANC spokesman
Ronnie Mamoepa said today.
</P>
