<HEADLINE> African Countries Eye Nigeria's Road Safety </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LAGOS, January 2 (Xinhua) -- Nigeria's Federal Road Safety
Commission (FRSC) said today its road safety schemes are soon to
be adopted by other African countries.
</P>
<P>
