within the context of Israeli escalation and threats which were
launched recently by Israeli officials that aim at killing the
peace process."
</P>
<P>
"The Mossad (Israeli intelligence) agents wanted to kill
innocent people and assassinate the joy in the children's eyes
with their ugly crime," it said.
</P>
<P>
An 11-member family was among the victims of the explosion,
reports said. 
