Hurghada, 506 kilometers southeast of Cairo, is a renowned Red
Sea resort attracting numerous tourists all the year round.
</P>
<P>
Those injured, all Russian, were rushed to Ras Gharib central
hospital for treatment and the prosecution was notified of the
accident, the agency said. 
