<HEADLINE> Tillstrom Beats Second Russian in Hardcourt Tennis </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
CANBERRA, January 3 (Xinhua) -- Unseeded Mikael Tillstrom of
Sweden upset Russian Andrei Cherkasov to move into the semifinals
of the U.S. dlrs 328,000 Australian Hardcourt tennis championships
with a 6-2, 6-4 win in Adelaide on Friday.
</P>
<P>
