understanding on bilateral trade and fishery and enhance their
cooperation in the fields of tourism and sciences, he said.
</P>
<P>
They also attached importance to frequent mutual visits by
high-ranking officials and businessmen to discuss latest
development in bilateral relations, Moerdiono added.
</P>
<P>
Meanwhile, the two countries agreed to open consulates in their
respective cities.
</P>
<P>
Chavalit arrived here Thursday at the invitation of President
Soeharto on a two-day visit to Indonesia.
</P>
<P>
This is Chavalit's first overseas visit since he was appointed
Thai prime minister on December 1, 1996. He left for home later in
the day.  
