simultaneously alerted and security precautions were taken.
</P>
<P>
The alleged bomb-on-board aircraft touched down at 8 PM last
night. After disembarkation of the passengers, the plane was
isolated at the far end of a runway.
</P>
<P>
However, a search conducted with the aid of sniffer dogs
revealed nothing.
</P>
<P>
During the scare, the main road into the airport was sealed
off by emergency vehicles as a precautionary measure, SABC
reported. 
